# components.rules.md

### A. Purpose
Enforce consistent component usage across all Khwarizmi interfaces using the **Syncfusion UI Kit — Material-3 Theme** as the sole component library. No custom or third-party components are permitted.

### B. Rules

**Source of Truth:**
- ALL UI components MUST come from the **Syncfusion UI Kit — Material-3 Theme** Figma library.
- Figma Community file: `https://www.figma.com/community/file/1454123774600129202/syncfusion-ui-kit-material-3-theme`
- In code, use the corresponding **Syncfusion React / JS / Blazor / Angular** component that maps to the Figma design.
- No custom-built components, no shadcn, no MUI, no Ant Design — Syncfusion only.
- All Syncfusion components must use the **Material-3 theme CSS** (`material3.css` or the customized output from Theme Studio).

